\/uploads\/2026\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-13-at-8.48.18-AM-1024x768.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-13-at-8.48.18-AM-200x150.jpeg 200w, https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-13-at-8.48.18-AM-300x225.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-13-at-8.48.18-AM-400x300.jpeg 400w, https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-13-at-8.48.18-AM-600x450.jpeg 600w, https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-13-at-8.48.18-AM-768x576.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-13-at-8.48.18-AM-800x600.jpeg 800w, https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-13-at-8.48.18-AM-1024x768.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-13-at-8.48.18-AM-1200x900.jpeg 1200w, https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-13-at-8.48.18-AM-1536x1152.jpeg 1536w, https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-13-at-8.48.18-AM.jpeg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>A proud and memorable moment in the history of our institution as our Founder and Director <strong>Dr A.Giridhar<\/strong> was conferred the prestigious <strong>AIOC S. S. Badrinath Endowment Award<\/strong> during the <strong>84th Annual Conference of the All India Ophthalmological Society<\/strong>, held at the Jaipur Exhibition &amp; Convention Centre on 12 March.<\/p>\n<p>This honour truly belongs to the entire team at Giridhar Eye Institute, recognizing their selfless service and unwavering commitment to eye care over the past three decades. It stands as an appreciation of the remarkable work carried out by our institution and a testament to our dedication to excellence in ophthalmology.<\/p>\n<p>Receiving this recognition at the national level, in the presence of over 10,000 ophthalmologists from across the country, is both humbling and inspiring. It motivates us to continue striving for greater impact and to serve our patients with even greater dedication in the years ahead.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; A proud and memorable moment in the history [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":10722,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"_uf_show_specific_survey":0,"_uf_disable_surveys":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[137],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-10721","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-events"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10721","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=10721"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10721\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":10736,"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10721\/revisions\/10736"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/10722"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\